
Create a VS Code task
    open Command Palette 
    choose “Tasks: Configure Task”
    Create tasks.json from template
    Others

to run the task :   Terminal --> Run Task --> task_name


Make it the default build task
    Open Command Palette 
    Tasks: Configure Default Build Task
    pick “Build LaTeX PDF (script)”.
    Now press Ctrl/Cmd+Shift+B to build the currently file.
